    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "What appeared week ago to be\na nice, tame, IadyIike election for\nis commissioners to draft the new\ncity charter has developed into a\nfirst class, interesting political\nscrap, in which some close finishes\nare looked for.\n\n\nThe voting this morning was a\ngame of cut and slash. in so far as\nthe two tickets in the field are con-\ncerned. The voter took his time to\nlook over the ballot. and the fact\nthat he took both tickets into the\nbooth with him and the time con-\nsumed in fixing up his ballot was\ntaken as an indication that he was\nvoting it to suit himself."
    }
